@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dfnnsa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(0.71)
    v0 = wp.abs(v1)
    v2 = (wp.cos(v1) + wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.34)))
    v2 = ((0.82 + (v1 + 0.54 / v1 + 0.07)) + wp.sin(v2))
    v2 = (0.08 + (v1 - (tmp + 0.88 / v1 + 0.46)))
    v1 = v2
    v1 = wp.cos(v1)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.45)))
    data[tid] = v0
